What you need to know:

The selection was apparently informed by the need to eliminate a bottleneck in the system that would have forced students to repeat classes.Prof Magoha has opted for a phased reopening, giving priority to the pioneer CBC class and KCPE and KCSE candidates.KCPE and KCSE exam candidates will now sit their tests in March and April 2021.More than a million learners will join pre-school, while an almost similar number will join secondary school.